item.title: CVE-2018-5505|2024-09-16T16:23:50.452Z -- f5%20networks%2C%20inc. -- big-ip%20%28asm%20and%20analytics%29
item.description: On F5 BIG-IP versions 13.1.0 - 13.1.0.3, when ASM and AVR are both provisioned, TMM may restart while processing DNS requests when the virtual server is configured with a DNS profile and the Protocol setting is set to TCP.
